  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to libraw</title>

    <para>
      <application>Libraw</application> is a library for reading RAW files
      obtained from digital photo cameras (CRW/CR2, NEF, RAF, DNG, and others). 
    </para>

    &lfs76_checked;

